[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]是一位[[英国|英国]]男导演、编剧及监制。他的导演生涯处女作是预算只有6000美元的新黑色犯罪惊悚片《[[追随|追随]]》（1998年）。<ref>{{cite news|title=How Memento Set the Framework for Christopher Nolan's Career|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/03/memento-is-a-precise-twisty-delight-15-years-on/473973/|work=[[大西洋_(雜誌)|The Atlantic]]|date=2016-03-16|accessdate=2019-12-09|last=Sims|first=David|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809124304/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/03/memento-is-a-precise-twisty-delight-15-years-on/473973/|archive-date=2016-08-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>这部电影用非线性叙事的手法讲述了一个年轻作家与黑社会犯罪纠缠在一起的故事。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/1998/film/reviews/following-1200453758/|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|title=Following|date=1998-05-11|accessdate=2019-12-09|last=Harvey|first=Dennis|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209141809/https://variety.com/1998/film/reviews/following-1200453758/|archive-date=2019-12-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>2000年，他导演了由[[盖·皮尔斯|盖·皮尔斯]]主演的惊悚片《[[凶心人|凶心人]]》，讲述了一个患有[[顺行性遗忘症|顺行性遗忘症]]的男人寻找杀死自己妻子的凶手的故事。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2001/03/16/movies/film-review-backward-reel-the-grisly-memories.html|work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|date=2001-03-16|accessdate=2019-12-07|last=Scott|first=A. O.|title=Film Review; Backward Reel the Grisly Memories|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191020180300/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/03/16/movies/film-review-backward-reel-the-grisly-memories.html|archive-date=2019-10-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>这部电影是他第一次与摄影师[[禾利·費斯達|禾利·費斯達]]合作。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2012/07/the-reason-christopher-nolan-films-look-like-christopher-nolan-films/260087/|work=The Atlantic|date=2012-07-23|accessdate=2019-12-13|title=The Reason Christopher Nolan Films Look Like Christopher Nolan Films|last=Buckwalter|first=Ian|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717224525/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2012/07/the-reason-christopher-nolan-films-look-like-christopher-nolan-films/260087/|archive-date=2016-07-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>这部电影和他的处女作一样也使用了非线性的叙事结构，是他的突破之作，<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/next-christopher-nolan-film-open-july-2020-1179373|work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2019-01-25|accessdate=2019-12-09|title=Next Christopher Nolan Film to Open in July 2020|last1=Couch|first=Aaron|last2=Kit|first2=Borys|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191122011839/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/next-christopher-nolan-film-open-july-2020-1179373|archive-date=2019-11-22|dead-url=no|author=|publisher=|language=|format=}}</ref>也受到了评论家的好评，并取得了令人惊讶的商业成功。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/sleeper-hits/|work=[[帝國雜誌|Empire]]|title=Sleeping Beauties: The Story Behind 12 Of Cinema's Unlikeliest Hits|last=White|first=James|date=2015-02-17|accessdate=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426102050/http://www.empireonline.com/movies/features/sleeper-hits/|archive-date=2016-04-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>凭借这部电影，诺兰获得了他的第一个{{tsl|en|Directors Guild of America Award for Outstanding Directing – Feature Film|美国导演工会奖电影类最佳导演奖}}提名。他同时参与了编剧，也获得了[[奥斯卡最佳原创剧本奖|奥斯卡最佳原创剧本奖]]的提名。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/in-contention/christopher-nolan-scores-his-first-ever-oscar-nomination-for-best-director-1202673364/|work=Variety|title=Christopher Nolan Scores His First-Ever Oscar Nomination for Best Director|last=Tapley|first=Kristopher|date=2018-01-23|accessdate=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://archive.is/20180123185650/http://variety.com/2018/film/in-contention/christopher-nolan-scores-his-first-ever-oscar-nomination-for-best-director-1202673364/|archive-date=2018-01-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The 74th Academy Awards|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2002|accessdate=2019-12-09|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[电影艺术与科学学院|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]]|language=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001230532/http://oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2002|archive-date=2016-10-01}}</ref>他下一部导演的作品是翻拍神秘惊悚片《[[白夜追兇|白夜追兇]]》（2002年），由[[艾尔·帕西诺|艾尔·帕西诺]]、[[羅賓·威廉斯|羅賓·威廉斯]]和[[希拉里·斯旺克|希拉里·斯旺克]]主演。<ref>{{cite web|title=Insomnia movie review & film summary (2002)|url=https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/insomnia-2002|accessdate=2019-12-09|date=2002-05-24|last=Ebert|first=Roger|publisher=Roger Ebert|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822143233/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/insomnia-2002|archive-date=2019-08-22}}</ref>这是他的第一部与[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]合作的电影，也获得了巨大的商业成功。<ref name="McNary">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/next-christopher-nolan-movie-release-date-1203118713/|work=Variety|title=Christopher Nolan's Next Movie Gets July 2020 Release Date|last=McNary|first=Dave|date=2019-01-25|accessdate=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190706061412/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/next-christopher-nolan-movie-release-date-1203118713/|archive-date=2019-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/laff-2012-dark-knight-rises-cinematographer-wally-pfister-imax-341329|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2012-06-24|accessdate=2019-12-09|title=LAFF 2012: 'Dark Knight Rises' Cinematographer Wally Pfister Discusses His Directorial Debut|last=Giardina|first=Carolyn|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328104220/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/laff-2012-dark-knight-rises-cinematographer-wally-pfister-imax-341329|archive-date=2019-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2005年，诺兰导演华纳兄弟的超级英雄电影《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》，由[[克里斯汀·貝爾|克里斯汀·貝爾]]主演，讲述了蝙蝠侠的起源。<ref>{{cite web|title=Batman Begins movie review and film summary (2005)|url=https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/batman-begins-2005|accessdate=2019-12-13|date=2005-06-13|last=Ebert|first=Roger|publisher=Roger Ebert|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208214254/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/batman-begins-2005|archive-date=2019-12-08}}</ref>2006年，他导演的心理惊悚片《[[頂尖對決|頂尖對決]]》中，克里斯汀·貝爾和[[休·傑克曼|休·傑克曼]]扮演了两位互相竞争的19世纪舞台魔术师。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/booksblog/2006/nov/15/allchangecantheprestigesu|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|last=Thompson|first=Sam|date=2006-11-15|accessdate=2019-12-09|title=Can The Prestige survive its Hollywood transformation?|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140926025126/http://www.theguardian.com/books/booksblog/2006/nov/15/allchangecantheprestigesu|archive-date=2014-09-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的下一部电影是《[[蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻|蝙蝠俠：開戰時刻]]》的续集《[[蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士]]》，在这部电影中，贝尔再次扮演蝙蝠侠，对抗[[希斯·萊傑|希斯·萊傑]]扮演的超级大反派[[小丑_(角色)|小丑]]。这部电影的全球票房超过10亿美元，是2008年的票房冠军。<ref>{{cite web|title=Worldwide Grosses|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100612053111/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/|archivedate=2010-06-12|dead-url=yes|accessdate=2020-09-06}}</ref>该片获得了8项[[第81屆奧斯卡金像獎|第81屆奧斯卡金像獎]]提名，诺兰第二次获得[[美国导演工会奖|美国导演工会奖]]提名。<ref>{{cite web|title=The 81st Academy Awards|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2009|accessdate=2019-12-13|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161102115358/https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2009|archive-date=2016-11-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2009/jan/09/christopher-nolan-nominated-dga-award|work=The Guardian|title=Nolan and Boyle nominated by DGA as Slumdog Millionaire sweeps Critics' Choice awards|accessdate=2019-12-13|date=2009-01-09|last=Child|first=Ben|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719020001/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2009/jan/09/christopher-nolan-nominated-dga-award|archive-date=2019-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年，诺兰执导了动作电影《[[盗梦空间|盗梦空间]]》，该片由[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]主演，莱昂纳多在片中饰演一位小偷，带领一个团队进入人的潜意识窃取信息。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/jul/18/inception-film-review-philip-french|work=[[觀察家報|The Observer]]|title=Inception|accessdate=2019-12-13|date=2010-07-18|last=French|first=Philip|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140519113502/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/jul/18/inception-film-review-philip-french|archive-date=2014-05-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>这部电影获得了[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]、[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]和[[金球奖|金球奖]]的最佳影片提名，诺兰第三次获得美国导演工会奖提名。<ref>{{cite web|title=The 83rd Academy Awards|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2011|accessdate=2019-12-13|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318133653/https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2011|archive-date=2020-03-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Film Awards 2011: Winners List|url=http://www.bafta.org/media-centre/press-releases/film-awards-2011-winners-list|accessdate=2019-12-13|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[英国电影学院奖|British Academy Film Awards]]|language=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190925120034/http://www.bafta.org/media-centre/press-releases/film-awards-2011-winners-list|archive-date=2019-09-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Inception|url=https://www.goldenglobes.com/film/inception|accessdate=2019-10-13|author=|date=|format=|publisher=[[好莱坞外国记者协会|Hollywood Foreign Press Association]]|language=|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213153005/https://www.goldenglobes.com/film/inception|archive-date=2019-12-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Darren Aronofsky, Christopher Nolan Among Directors Guild Nominees|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/darren-aronofsky-christopher-nolan-directors-69852|accessdate=2019-12-13|last=Kilday|first=Gregg|work=The Hollywood Reporter|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191213152955/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/darren-aronofsky-christopher-nolan-directors-69852|archive-date=2019-12-13}}</ref>

2012年，他执导了《[[蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士]]》的续集《[[蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起|蝙蝠侠：黑暗骑士崛起]]》，该片全球总票房超过10亿美元。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-milestone-dark-knight-rises-warner-bros-christopher-nolan-christian-bale-367476|work=The Hollywood Reporter|title=Box Office Milestone: 'Dark Knight Rises' Crosses $1 Billion Worldwide|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|date=2012-09-02|accessdate=2019-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207050555/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-milestone-dark-knight-rises-warner-bros-christopher-nolan-christian-bale-367476|archive-date=2019-12-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年，他制作了[[查克·史奈德|查克·史奈德]]的超级英雄电影《[[超人：钢铁之躯|超人：钢铁之躯]]》。2014年，他导演了由[[马修·麦康纳|马修·麦康纳]]、[[安妮·海瑟薇|安妮·海瑟薇]]和[[杰西卡·查斯坦|杰西卡·查斯坦]]主演的科幻电影《[[星际穿越|星际穿越]]》，该片获得了[[土星獎最佳科幻電影|土星獎最佳科幻電影]]奖。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2015/scene/vpage/saturn-awards-walking-dead-the-flash-guardians-of-the-galaxy-interstellar-1201529054/|work=Variety|title='Guardians of the Galaxy,' 'The Walking Dead,' 'Interstellar' Shine at Saturn Awards|last=Cohen|first=David S.|date=2015-06-26|accessdate=2019-12-13|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160104222605/http://variety.com/2015/scene/vpage/saturn-awards-walking-dead-the-flash-guardians-of-the-galaxy-interstellar-1201529054/|archive-date=2016-01-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年，诺兰执导了战争电影《[[敦刻尔克|敦刻尔克]]》，凭借该片他首次获得[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|奥斯卡最佳导演奖]]提名。<ref>{{cite web|title=The 90th Academy Awards|url=https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2018|accessdate=2019-12-13|publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180310211235/https://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/2018|archive-date=2018-03-10}}</ref>2020年，他执导的间谍电影《[[TENET天能|TENET天能]]》上映。<ref>{{Cite web|title='Tenet' Will Release Internationally in August Ahead of U.S. Debut|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/box-office/tenet-release-date-international-movie-theaters-1234717187/|date=2020-07-27|last=Rubin|first=Rebecca|access-date=2020-08